I have updated the code to include Dynamic Tabs below the wheel.
Now, inside the Dashboard, you can switch between "Refer & Earn" and "Leaderboard" without reloading the page. I also updated the Language Settings so these new tabs translate automatically when you change the language.
Complete Updated Code
